Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:46.55,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ginko committed a grave crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.55,0:00:47.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was Sumika's--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:54.43,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.43,0:00:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,...never forgive bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll ruin bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.81,0:01:07.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Growl!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:23.08,Main,,0,0,0,,We hated you from the beginning--\Nand loved you from the beginning, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,And so we wanted to become\Ntrue friends with you. To cross the wall...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:36.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikumaaaaaaaaa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:38.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Yurikuma Arashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,"THE FUTURE OF THE GIRLS"\N{\i1}Viens avec moi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.52,0:01:47.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Church chimes echo in the distance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.82,0:01:50.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Offer up a prayer and betray today{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.65,0:01:56.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wander in a dark forest, then become{\i0}\N{\i1}the morning moon at the Wall of Severance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.16,0:01:58.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't join the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:02.66,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Once I've made you stickier{\i0}\N{\i1}with sweet, thin honey{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.66,0:02:06.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, approve me, I'll be a good girl{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Picture-book pages dancing on{\i0}\N{\i1}the breeze shake up shadowy memories{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:18.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.43,0:02:24.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be waiting you-know-where,{\i0}\N{\i1}in an empty world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if everything falls apart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.32,0:02:36.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if you have to gracefully writhe,{\i0}\N{\i1}even if you have to bend space-time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.41,0:02:39.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Find me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:51.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flower petals will slowly{\i0}\N{\i1}enfold us on a starry night{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.13,0:02:55.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:58.34,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.14,0:03:07.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}J'ai besoin de toi{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:16.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Girls, this is way bad! People are\Nsaying another bear was here yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.57,0:03:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,But I heard it was exterminated right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:24.08,Main,,0,0,0,,That same girl shot it, right?\NThe Invisible Storm one?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but--and this is way secret--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.33,0:03:30.38,Main,,0,0,0,,apparently that bear's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.46,0:04:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Door to Friendship, you silly girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:19.55,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Door to Friendship・(Place)"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Now I've gotten rid of the nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:35.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko Yurishiro... You're the girl Reia\Ngave her pendant to on that stormy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.53,Main,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}foolish {\i0}girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.07,0:04:42.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Instead of getting love,\Nyou fell into the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.53,0:04:44.53,Main,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.53,0:04:49.33,Main,,0,0,0,,You knew Lulu Yurigasaki loved you,\Nbut you pretended not to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:52.13,Main,,0,0,0,,And then you tried to abandon her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.13,0:04:54.46,Main,,0,0,0,,You're paying the price of that sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Guess what, Reia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:05.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Your daughter Kureha Tsubaki\Nis about to be my bride-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:07.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.18,0:05:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.64,0:05:12.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:15.77,Main,,0,0,0,,...I'm going to eat Kureha Tsubaki! Purrowr!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.95,0:05:26.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're alive. For now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.92,0:05:35.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I surprise you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:39.05,Main,,0,0,0,,You're... supposed to be dead, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, I died.\NYou're the only one who can see me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:53.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's say I'm a ghost named "Desire,"\Ndwelling inside you right... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:57.19,Main,,0,0,0,,That'll do for an explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:05:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,The Door to Friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.36,0:06:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,The center of the sky that divides\Nthe worlds of moon and forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:09.08,Main,,0,0,0,,The place where true love is tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:14.87,Main,,0,0,0,,So, tell me--how did you kill Sumika Izumino?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.13,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,I say we come early tomorrow\Nmorning and fix the flowerbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.13,0:06:25.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll help, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:27.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Yurizono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, okay? You, too, Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.18,0:06:31.85,Main,,0,0,0,,A-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Who did that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I sensed it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:49.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I had a rival at this school\Nwho was after Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:53.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Another bear in human form\Nbesides Konomi and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.62,0:06:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,If I didn't hurry,\Nanother bear would beat me to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:06:59.79,Main,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.88,0:07:01.55,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:04.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm headed this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:05.97,Main,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.97,0:07:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Listen, Izumino, about tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.64,0:07:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't the two of us arrange a surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,A surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.64,0:07:20.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I know someone with young lilies\Nin bloom who'd probably give us some.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.86,0:07:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,I bet we can have them by tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:24.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.53,0:07:28.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. So let's beat Tsubaki\Nto school tomorrow morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:32.95,Main,,0,0,0,,and fill the flowerbed with lots of new lilies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:35.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What? But that would...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.00,0:07:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,It'll be just like magic!\NI'm sure Tsubaki will be thrilled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,That girl would've done {\i1}anything{\i0}\Nif I said it was for Kureha Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Now come on, be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.85,0:08:04.94,Main,,0,0,0,,You found out that I was\Ntargeting Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:07.19,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.70,0:08:18.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I knew all along that you were following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.33,0:08:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you like those flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:24.84,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.84,0:08:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You're the exchange student...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.55,0:08:32.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Sniff, sniff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:38.35,Main,,0,0,0,,They smell nice, don't they?\NDo you like lilies, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:42.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Lilies remind me of a special memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:48.74,Main,,0,0,0,,A special memory with a friend I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:53.99,Main,,0,0,0,,I won't back down on love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.99,0:08:57.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Because the love she gave me,\Nno one can take away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,It was probably weird for me to tell\Nyou that when we've only just met...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:10.72,Main,,0,0,0,,You were jealous of her, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.72,0:09:16.72,Main,,0,0,0,,The love you wanted so badly from Kureha\Nhad already been given to another girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.52,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"That Fateful Morning・(History)"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.85,0:09:30.03,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet you went to her again,\Nwithout even telling your partner your intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.45,0:09:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Why, to warn her about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.70,0:09:37.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. That was my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.04,0:09:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh no, I can't believe I lost it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.80,0:09:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for finding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:58.81,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad! You know, this is the second time\Nsomeone's found this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.81,0:10:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I lost it the day of the entrance ceremony, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the friend I told you\Nabout yesterday who found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,She... found...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.48,0:10:16.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. This pin brought me friendship and love.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.32,0:10:18.78,Main,,0,0,0,,It's my special charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:25.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, Yurishiro!\NNow, I've got to hurry, or I'll be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.46,0:10:26.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:36.34,Main,,0,0,0,,I was the one she found first, growl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:44.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, if you'd stopped her then,\NSumika Izumino wouldn't have had to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:49.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki wouldn't\Nhave had to lose a dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,To me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:54.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumika was in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.07,0:11:03.75,Main,,0,0,0,,We exclude those in our way.\NWe ought to be honest about what we want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:10.42,Main,,0,0,0,,So that's it... I {\i1}wanted {\i0}Sumika to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.59,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Izumino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.30,0:11:19.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:20.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Bear shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:24.64,Main,,0,0,0,,It's such a nice morning. And I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.64,0:11:25.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Chomp, chomp, grawr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:33.36,Main,,0,0,0,,You witnessed me attacking\NSumika Izumino, and you just let her die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.36,0:11:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,You could've saved her, but you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who ate her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:43.79,Main,,0,0,0,,But the one who {\i1}killed {\i0}her...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,...was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:49.58,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right! In that moment,\Nyou were a slave of desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Jealousy drove you to a terrible crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm a criminal-bear, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.59,0:12:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. But is there any creature\Nwho doesn't sin in order to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.68,0:12:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki forgot you, her friend,\Nand gave her love to Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.14,0:12:15.94,Main,,0,0,0,,Now listen closely: Only one thing\Nis certain in this world, and it's not friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:20.28,Main,,0,0,0,,It's me--desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:25.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Love is a savage emotion.\NTo love someone is to rule them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:30.29,Main,,0,0,0,,To want to become one with them\Nso badly that you consume them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:33.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you something you'll want to know--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.04,0:12:37.76,Main,,0,0,0,,There's another bear at that school besides us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:40.30,Main,,0,0,0,,A very cunning bear, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:45.81,Main,,0,0,0,,She got Kureha to kill me,\Nand she got Lulu Yurigasaki to betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:51.23,Main,,0,0,0,,I hate to admit it, but that bitch-bear\Nhad all of us dancing to her tune.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.23,0:12:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,--She's after Kureha Tsubaki right now.\N--Chomp, chomp, purrowr. Chomp, chomp, purrowr.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:13:01.61,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry,\Nyou'll lose her forever this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:11.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Now, become one with me.\NIt's time to prove your love!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.35,0:13:28.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Grawr grawr grawr, graw-ha-ha-ha-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.39,0:13:33.19,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear opens!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:41.86,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm going to eat her, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:02.26,Main,,0,0,0,,These photos were discovered\Nin the locker of Kaoru Harishima,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,who recently died in a bear attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:12.52,Main,,0,0,0,,As you can see, Konomi Yurikawa\Nwas actually a bear disguised as a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.90,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Chouko Oki・(Yuri)"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.90,0:14:21.44,MainTop,,0,0,0,,This is way scary. Bears got across\Nthe wall pretending to be human,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:25.62,Main,,0,0,0,,and they've eaten our friends one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:30.95,Main,,0,0,0,,We all see what this means, agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:37.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, there is a bear\Nin this class--a bear among {\i1}us{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.04,0:14:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears {\i1}way {\i0}stick out from our crowd!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.80,0:14:44.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears refuse to fit in with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Bears are evil, unable to follow social cues!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.93,0:14:48.68,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Can't Follow Social Cues = Evil = Bear・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.73,Main,,0,0,0,,It's started up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:56.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yep. But Kureha Tsubaki is attending this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.31,0:15:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,They make her a friend at this late date?\NHave they canceled her exclusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Those girls are always looking\Nfor some "evil" to exclude.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to them whether\Nthe evil is a person or a bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,The ritual of banding\Ntogether to exclude someone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,makes the invisible connection\Ncalled "us" feel real to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.18,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the sexy way. Shaba-da-doo--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.60,0:15:33.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Shall I put in another coin?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:36.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:38.81,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.81,0:15:41.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Let us begin the Exclusion Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.23,0:15:42.65,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Exclusion Ceremony・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Please name the bear lurking among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.99,0:15:50.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Let's search bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:56.33,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"The Invisible Storm・(Exclusion)"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:23.32,Main,,0,0,0,,"Ginko Yurishiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.36,0:16:27.70,Main,,0,0,0,,People who shelter bears are accomplices!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:31.45,MainTop,,0,0,0,,"Ginko Yurishiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.95,0:16:34.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.70,0:16:38.04,Main,,0,0,0,,...what should I have done that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:40.83,Main,,0,0,0,,"Flashback"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Lulu...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:48.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Kure-{\i1}chin{\i0}, I know what Ginko did to Sumika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.42,0:16:49.72,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.72,0:16:53.10,Main,,0,0,0,,That's right. Ginko committed a grave crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.10,0:16:56.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko was Sumika's killer's accomplice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:03.11,Main,,0,0,0,,It's true, growl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:07.74,Main,,0,0,0,,I killed Sumika Izumino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.24,0:17:21.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko Yurizono killed Sumika.\NI know that for sure, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Why would Ginko say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:29.09,Main,,0,0,0,,What's the truth, and what's a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.30,0:17:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,"Incoming Call: Blocked Number"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.18,0:17:40.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.68,0:17:43.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Is your love the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:46.82,Main,,0,0,0,,This is a challenge from the Wall of Severance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:52.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki, if your\Nlove is true, go to the lily bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.78,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear is waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.78,0:17:58.83,Main,,0,0,0,,So she's there? Ginko's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.83,0:18:04.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Give yourself over to the bears,\Nand your love will be approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:09.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll going to go talk to Ginko.\NI'll find out the truth this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:16.10,Main,,0,0,0,,To think she masqueraded as us\Nto make a prank call to Kureha Tsubaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:19.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika Hakonaka is guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:25.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, today was the whole\Nreason for her contract with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,so she's probably ready for\Nthe consequences. Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.36,0:18:32.86,Main,,0,0,0,,All shall be as Kumaria wills it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.82,Main,,0,0,0,,That's the sexy way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:36.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Shaba-da-doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:43.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko, what happened between us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:46.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I want to know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:55.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia, do you remember that stormy night?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.35,Main,,0,0,0,,I ate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:19:01.31,Main,,0,0,0,,To put you in the box of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.31,0:19:06.65,Main,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't fulfilled. I was still empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.65,0:19:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, all your love had been given to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.03,0:19:16.11,Main,,0,0,0,,So I decided to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:21.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait until that girl who stole\Nyour love from me grew up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.04,0:19:26.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait as your love\Ngradually blossomed inside her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.29,0:19:30.21,Main,,0,0,0,,And I did, in a blank world robbed of all color.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.21,0:19:33.26,Main,,0,0,0,,I waited, and waited, and waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.26,0:19:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.18,0:19:43.31,Main,,0,0,0,,The flower bloomed. Today, I eat your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:47.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Today I eat Kureha Tsubaki. Purrowr!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:54.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ginko! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.03,0:20:00.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Pant, pant, purrowr...\NPant, pant, purrowr...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.74,0:20:02.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Purrowrrrrr.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,This is wrong. This bear isn't Ginko.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:12.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Reia, she looks just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:17.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Her eyes, her hair... She even has your smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.05,0:20:22.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Kureha Tsubaki, give your love to me! Purrowr!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:26.43,Main,,0,0,0,,You and I are going to become one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.57,0:20:41.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Now take my kiss, Kureha.\NThis is a kiss for the bride-in-the-box.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Pur-ro-rowrrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:51.84,Main,,0,0,0,,That was a way close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:53.96,Main,,0,0,0,,You're... Oki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.92,Main,,0,0,0,,The bear ran away! After it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.51,0:21:00.01,Main,,0,0,0,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:08.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.18,0:21:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika... Yuriika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Yuriika? Yuriika!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:20.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Reia... you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:22.41,Main,,0,0,0,,I missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.41,0:21:29.87,Main,,0,0,0,,This day is all I've thought of,\Never since that night I ate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.87,0:21:35.13,Main,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to return to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:40.17,Main,,0,0,0,,In a box in the middle of my drawers...\N{\i1}The Moon Girl and the Forest Girl{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:44.51,Main,,0,0,0,,The box has the rest of that picture book in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.14,0:21:51.48,Main,,0,0,0,,It was the dream of our love\Nthat never materialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,So I wanted it so desperately, I stole it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:21:58.53,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.03,0:22:09.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right. That's their destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.70,0:22:21.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Their rightful future...\NSay, Reia... I really... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.55,0:22:25.43,Main,,0,0,0,,We'll be friends forever, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. Friends forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.22,0:22:32.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:08.72,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}On the boundary that severed{\i0}\N{\i1}ripe moon from sleeping forest{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.72,0:23:15.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Break the law God shackles us with and smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.39,0:23:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I turned away from the bleating flock{\i0}\N{\i1}of shadows and howled my bloodthirsty ego{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.44,0:23:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here amidst the Invisible Storm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:32.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Overflowing honey and soul{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.41,0:23:35.87,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to rend silk with my fangs{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:42.92,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid you'll vanish{\i0}\N{\i1}like the world's last ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.92,0:23:49.76,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The savage beast inside me{\i0}\N{\i1}tore out the throat of innocence{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.76,0:23:59.81,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come on, shoot me through the heart{\i0}\N{\i1}with your sweet-scented Barrett of love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.33,0:24:21.75,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe Miss Yuriika\Nwas the bear who killed Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.75,0:24:27.01,Main,,0,0,0,,It's their destiny... Their rightful future...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.01,0:24:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,This is Ginko's and my future?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.01,0:24:33.56,Main,,0,0,0,,No... that's impossible!
